              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Tritium was converted to water in a closed",
                "system and its activity measured by liquid",
                "scintillation techniques."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma activity of the barium sample was",
                "measured using a 5 in. sodium iodide scintillator.",
                "The  counting efficiency for the 140Ba in the sodium",
                "iodide crystal spectrometer was determined by counting",
                "equal aliquots of a separated 140Ba solution",
                "simultaneously in the sodium iodide crystal",
                "spectrometer and in the \"Tri-Carb\" liquid scintillation",
                "spectrometer."
              ]
